2800.name: Jax's Diary
2800.description: A diary that bodyguard Jax has given, saying that it will aid in the search for Solt's and Makel's maps.

2801.name: 1st Torn Map Piece
2801.description: A piece of the map that belonged to the former lord's guard Solt. Gather 4 of these.

2802.name: 2nd Torn Map Piece
2802.description: A piece of the map that belonged to the former lord's guard Makel. Gather 4 of these.

2803.name: Solt's Map
2803.description: A map where the name of the former lord's guard Solt is written.

2804.name: Makel's Map
2804.description: A map where the name of the former lord's guard Makel is written.

2805.name: Combined Map
2805.description: Using the map (alt-m), find the hiding place of the lord's gold bar.

2806.name: Rusted Key
2806.description: A rusty copper key discovered while digging under the tree indicated on the map.

2807.name: Gold Bar
2807.description: A gold bar stamped with Duke Ashton's seal. Take this to Alex.

2808.name: Alex's Recommend
2808.description: A recommendation written by Alex. Take this to Master Luther.

2809.name: Mark of Searcher
2809.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Searcher. An occupation change related item.

2810.name: Report of Perrin
2810.description: Take this report and go seek Perrin in Gludin Harbor.

2811.name: Kristina's Letter
2811.description: A letter given by Saint Kristina. Deliver this to Master Sorius.

2812.name: Picture of Windy
2812.description: A picture of Windy. Take this drawing to Windy.

2813.name: Golden Statue
2813.description: The reward given by the head of the orphanage. Something good happens if this is in possession?

2814.name: Windy's Pebbles
2814.description: A pebble that Windy has picked up from the Wastelands. Take this to Gupu, the head of the orphanage near Gludio.

2815.name: Order of Sorius
2815.description: Take these orders and show them to Daurin, who is located west of the Orc Barracks.

2816.name: 1st Secret Letter
2816.description: The documents of Leto lizardmen. Gather all of the letters and deliver them to Saint Kristina.

2817.name: 2nd Secret Letter
2817.description: The documents of Leto lizardmen. Gather all of the letters and deliver them to Saint Kristina.

2818.name: 3rd Secret Letter
2818.description: The documents of Leto lizardmen. Gather all of the letters and deliver them to Saint Kristina.

2819.name: 4th Secret Letter
2819.description: The documents of Leto lizardmen. Gather all of the letters and deliver them to Saint Kristina.

2820.name: Mark of Healer
2820.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Test of the Healer. An occupation change related item.

2821.name: Mark of Reformer
2821.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Reformer. An occupation change related item.

2822.name: Book of Reform
2822.description: A book received from Priestess Pupina. Go to the Execution Grounds and slay the nameless undeads with the power of light.

2823.name: Letter of Introduction
2823.description: A letter introducing Priestess Pupina. Take this and meet with to Preacher Sla of the Wastelands.

2824.name: Sla's Letter
2824.description: A letter given by Sla. Take this to Katari, who is near the waterfalls of the Neutral Zone.

2825.name: Greetings
2825.description: A letter sent by Sla to her disciples. Go to the Orc Village, Dwarven Village, and Talking Island in this order.

2826.name: Ol Mahum's Money
2826.description: Ol Mahum currency given by the themselves as a reward. For what...? Nobody knows.

2827.name: Katari's Letter
2827.description: Katari's reply letter to Sla. Collect 3 reply letters from Sla's disciples and deliver them to Sla.

2828.name: Nyakuri's Letter
2828.description: Nyakuri's reply letter to Sla. Collect 3 reply letters from Sla's disciples and deliver them to Sla.

2829.name: Undead List
2829.description: Skeleton archer, skeleton lord, skeleton marksman, misery skeleton, silent horror.

2830.name: Ramus's Letter
2830.description: A reply letter sent by Ramus to Sla. Deliver this to Sla after meeting all of Sla's disciples.

2831.name: Ripped Diary
2831.description: Diaries containing the final words of young women unfairly killed during the witch hunts of Duke Byron Ashton. Collect 7 of them.

2832.name: Huge Nail
2832.description: The large nail that was embedded in Aruraune's skull. Take this to Priestess Pupina at Town of Giran.

2833.name: Letter of Betrayer
2833.description: A letter given by an Ol Mahum Betrayer. Take it to Katari in the swamp area of the Dark Forest.

2834.name: Bone Fragment
2834.description: Bone pieces of a silent horror. Take this, along with the rest of the undead bone fragments, to Ramus.

2835.name: Bone Fragment
2835.description: A bone fragment of a skeleton lord. Take this, along with the rest of the undead bone fragments, to Ramus.

2836.name: Bone Fragment
2836.description: A bone fragment of a skeleton marksman. Take this, along with the rest of the undead bone fragments, to Ramus.

2837.name: Bone Fragment
2837.description: A bone fragment from a misery skeleton. Take it along with other bone fragments of the undead to Ramus.

2838.name: Bone Fragment
2838.description: A bone fragment of a skeleton archer. Take this, along with the rest of the undead bone fragments, to Ramus.

2839.name: Bone Fragment
2839.description: A bone fragment of a skeleton. Take this, along with the rest of the undead bone fragments, to Ramus.

2840.name: Mark of Magus
2840.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Magus. An item for occupational change.

2841.name: Rukal's Letter
2841.description: A letter sent by Bard Rukal to Parina of the Village of Gludin.

2842.name: Parina's Letter
2842.description: A letter sent by Parina to Elder Casian. The letter makes inquiries regarding the singing flower.

2843.name: Lilac Charm
2843.description: A protection charm created by Elder Casian. Take this and seek out the 3 types of singing flowers.

2844.name: 1st Golden Seed
2844.description: The seed of the singing flower, which absorbs blood in order to bloom. Gather 3 of these and take them to Bard Rukal.

2845.name: 2nd Golden Seed
2845.description: The seed of the singing flower, which absorbs blood in order to bloom. Gather 3 of these and take them to Bard Rukal.

2846.name: 3rd Golden Seed
2846.description: The seed of the singing flower, which absorbs blood in order to bloom. Gather 3 of these and take them to Bard Rukal.

2847.name: Score of Elements
2847.description: A music score sheet given by Bard Rukal. Take this and find the 4 elemental tones.

2848.name: Dazzling Drop
2848.description: A dazzling, tear-shaped jewel. Gather 20 of these and take them to the Water Undine.

2849.name: Flame Crystal
2849.description: A crystal obtained from the ghost fire. Gather 5 of these and take them to the Flame Salamander.

2850.name: Harpy's Feather
2850.description: The feather of a slain harpy. Gather 20 of these and take them to the Wind Sylph.

2851.name: Wyrm's Wingbone
2851.description: The wingbone of a slain Wyrm. Gather 10 of these and take them to the Wind Sylph.

2852.name: Windsus Mane
2852.description: The mane of a slain Windsus. Gather 10 of these and take them to the Wind Sylph.

2853.name: Enchanted Monster Eye Shell
2853.description: The skin of a slain enchanted eye. Gather 10 of these and take them to the Earth Snake.

2854.name: Enchanted Golem Powder
2854.description: Stone powder obtained after slaying an enchanted stone golem. Gather 10 of these and take them to the Earth Snake.

2855.name: Enchanted Iron Golem Shard
2855.description: A fragment of a destroyed enchanted iron golem. Gather 10 of these and take them to the Earth Snake.

2856.name: Tone of Water
2856.description: One that comprises the beautiful harmony of the 4 elemental tones. Take this to Bard Rukal in the Town of Dion.

2857.name: Tone of Fire
2857.description: One that comprises the beautiful harmony of the four elemental tones. Take this to Bard Rukal in the Town of Dion.

2858.name: Tone of Wind
2858.description: One that comprise the beautiful harmony of the four elemental tones. Take this to Bard Rukal in the Town of Dion.

2859.name: Tone of Earth
2859.description: One that comprise the beautiful harmony of the four elemental tones. Take this to Bard Rukal in the Town of Dion.

2860.name: Salamander Charm
2860.description: A charm of agreement given by the Flame Salamander. It promises to give the tone of fire in return for 5 flame crystals.

2861.name: Sylph Charm
2861.description: A charm of agreement given by the Wind Sylph. It promises to give the tone of wind in return for materials gathered from the harpy, Wyrm, and Windsus.

2862.name: Undine Charm
2862.description: A charm of agreement given by the Water Undine. It promises to give the tone of water in return for 20 dazzling drops.

2863.name: Serpent Charm
2863.description: A charm of agreement given by the Earth Snake. It promises to give the tone of earth in return for slaying the enchanted monsters in the surroundings of the Ivory Tower.

2864.name: Recommendation of Balanki
2864.description: A recommendation given by Silver Scale's Balanki. Gather all 3 recommendations and visit Lockirin of the Iron Gate.

2865.name: Recommendation of Filaur
2865.description: A recommendation given by Filaur of the Gray Pillar. Gather all 3 recommendations and seek out Lockirin of the Iron Gate.

2866.name: Recommendation of Arin
2866.description: A recommendation given by Black Anvil's Arin. Gather all 3 recommendations and go to Lockirin of the Iron Gate.

2867.name: Mark of Maestro
2867.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Maestro. An occupation change related item.

2868.name: Letter of Solder Detachment
2868.description: A letter from Captain Croto that promises to send soldiers. Deliver this to Lockirin of the Iron Gate.

2869.name: Paint of Kamuru
2869.description: A painting of Kamuru. Go to the Cave of Trials in the orc kingdom to seek him out.

2870.name: Necklace of Kamuru
2870.description: A necklace worn by Kamuru. Deliver this to Captain Croto.

2871.name: Paint of Teleport Device
2871.description: A drawing of a teleport device. Recover this device from Master Toma.

2872.name: Teleport Device
2872.description: A teleport device given by Master Toma. Deliver this to Black Anvil's Arin.

2873.name: Architecture of Cruma
2873.description: A simple explanation of Cruman architecture. Take this to the research team stationed at the entrance of the Cruma Tower.

2874.name: Report of Cruma
2874.description: A report recording the results of investigations made by the Cruma research team. Deliver this to Eldar Filaur.

2875.name: Ingredients of Antidote
2875.description: Gather 10 stinger wasp needles, 10 marsh spider webs, and 10 leech bloods and deliver them to Researcher Lorain.

2876.name: Stinger Wasp Needle
2876.description: Gather 10 of these and deliver them along with the other ingredients to Researcher Lorain.

2877.name: Marsh Spider's Web
2877.description: Gather 10 of these and deliver them along with the other ingredients to Researcher Lorain.

2878.name: Leech Blood
2878.description: Gather 10 of these and deliver them along with the other ingredients to Researcher Lorain.

2879.name: Mark of Warspirit
2879.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Test of the War Spirit. An item for occupational change.

2880.name: Vendetta Totem
2880.description: A totem given to the Orcs who seek to punish betrayers of their race. Take this and hunt the Tamlin Orcs.

2881.name: Tamlin Orc Head
2881.description: The head of a slain Tamlin Orc. Gather 13 of these and take them to Seer Somak.

2882.name: Warspirit Totem
2882.description: A totem used in the Ritual of the War Spirit. Take this to Ancestor Martankus in the Cave of Trials.

2883.name: Orim's Contract
2883.description: I will give you Braki's remains in return for 10 porta eyes, 10 excuro scales and 10 mordeo talons.

2884.name: Porta's Eye
2884.description: A jewel pried from the porta's eye. Gather 10 of these and take them to Orim of the Shadow.

2885.name: Excuro's Scale
2885.description: The scales of an excuro. Gather 10 of these and take them to Orim of the Shadow.

2886.name: Mordeos Talon
2886.description: The talons of a mordeo. Gather 10 of these and take them to Orim of the Shadow.

2887.name: Braki's Remains
2887.description: The remains of Braki, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 3 remains, to Seer Somak.

2888.name: Pekiron's Totem
2888.description: A guardian totem received from Seer Pekiron. Take this and go to the Leto lizardman shamans and chiefs to recover Tonar's remains.

2889.name: Tonar's Skull
2889.description: The skull of Tonar, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Pekiron.

2890.name: Tonar's Rib Bone
2890.description: The rib bones of Tonar, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Pekiron.

2891.name: Tonar's Spine
2891.description: The spine bones of Tonar, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Pekiron.

2892.name: Tonar's Arm Bone
2892.description: The arm bones of Tonar, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Pekiron.

2893.name: Tonar's Thigh Bone
2893.description: The thigh bones of Tonar, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Pekiron.

2894.name: Tonar's Remains
2894.description: The remains of Tonar, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the other 3 heroes' remains, to Seer Somak.

2895.name: Manakia's Totem
2895.description: A totem received from Seer Manakia. Take this and go to the medusas and Stenoa, the gorgon queen, to recover Hermodt's remains.

2896.name: Hermodt's Skull
2896.description: The skull of Hermodt, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Manakia.

2897.name: Hermodt's Rib Bone
2897.description: The rib bones of Hermodt, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Manakia.

2898.name: Hermodt's Spine
2898.description: The spine bones of Hermodt, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Manakia.

2899.name: Hermodt's Arm Bone
2899.description: The arm bones of Hermodt, an ancient Orc hero. Take this, along with the additional 4 remains, to Seer Manakia.
